Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs20\shad1\c&H70D8FB&\fn迷你简汉真广标\b0\pos(220,306)}漫迪字幕组倾情奉献\N\N——·旗木译制·——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这事儿你没想清楚\N{\fnArial\fs16}I don't think you've thought this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,到了机场遇见人质劫持怎么办?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What do you do with the hostages when you get to the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们跟我来呗\N{\fnArial\fs16}They're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可以考虑飞机派对\N{\fnArial\fs16}We're talking party plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,一路嗨飞利比亚\N{\fnArial\fs16}All the way to Libya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita 真是太棒了 好为你们高兴啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Rita, that's so wonderful. I'm so happy for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你和Erin你们俩\N{\fnArial\fs16}You and Erin both.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你要不自己遛弯儿吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Ah, you'd better take a hike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈跟我Rita姨打电话呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}My mom's talking to my Aunt Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,气氛不会很开心\N{\fnArial\fs16}This isn't going to be pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.97,0:01:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,了解 回见好吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Gotcha. Later, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,情况有待观察\N{\fnArial\fs16}That remains to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,太难以置信了 小Erin都要结婚了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I can't believe it. Little Erin getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她应该没有被逼婚 但愿吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}She's not rushing into this, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没没 怎么会了啦 二十一岁...\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, no, no, of course not. Twenty-one is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪里阴阳怪气了 真是的 Rita\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm not implying anything, for goodness sake, Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是... 太兴奋了嘛 哪里?\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm just... this is so exciting! Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好的呀\N{\fnArial\fs16}That sounds lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜老妈给你掏这笔钱? 不 不...\N{\fnArial\fs16}I presume Mom's footing the bill? No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你Erin表姐要结婚了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Your cousin Erin is getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我听出来了\N{\fnArial\fs16}So I gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可得花上一大笔银子啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}You know there'll be hell to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,大家伙应该都听到这个好消息了吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, I guess you all heard the wonderful news.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小Erin要结婚了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Little Erin is getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,在利威尔的温莎山度假村\N{\fnArial\fs16}At the Windsor Hills Resort in Leeville.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:02:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我去 这可得烧Rita不少银子喔\N{\fnArial\fs16}Whoa-ho! That'll set Rita back a pretty penny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,毛哇 我妈掏\N{\fnArial\fs16}Not Rita. Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.23,0:02:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,铁公鸡为了她最好闺女的宝贝孩子 情愿拔光毛\N{\fnArial\fs16}Nothing but the best for her favorite daughter's darling offspring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,温莎山\N{\fnArial\fs16}Windsor Hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿可有大名鼎鼎的十三球洞诶\N{\fnArial\fs16}They've got that legendary thirteenth hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.22,0:02:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 Jake 是婚礼 别想高尔夫\N{\fnArial\fs16}Forget it, Jake. No golf. Wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经开始遗憾参加不了婚礼了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm almost sorry I'm going to miss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,正相反 宝贝儿\N{\fnArial\fs16}On the contrary, sweetie:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你和Quinn要去当伴娘\N{\fnArial\fs16}you and Quinn are going to be bridesmaids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这事一万个准\N{\fnArial\fs16}I made sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,伴娘?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Bridesmaids?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,要是裙子颜色不搭 我能染头发嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Can I dye my hair if the dress doesn't match?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是天意弄人啊 我 居然要做伴娘\N{\fnArial\fs16}What a hideous twist of fate. Me, a bridesmaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦没那么糟啦 我知道 没错\N{\fnArial\fs16}Aw, it won't be that bad, I mean, sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你得穿那种桃色花边裙\N{\fnArial\fs16}you'll have to wear some frilly peach-color dress
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,变成马戏团怪人那种样子\N{\fnArial\fs16}that makes you look like a circus freak,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还会被爱不释手的怪蜀黍捏脸\N{\fnArial\fs16}and you'll be pinched by incontinent old uncles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,以为你现在还只有六岁 还会...\N{\fnArial\fs16}who still think you're still six years old, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,到咯\N{\fnArial\fs16}Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 本店只提供婚礼服务 不做葬礼\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm sorry, we only do weddings, not funerals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不骗你 我爱葬礼更胜一筹\N{\fnArial\fs16}Believe me, I'd prefer a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 不想结婚可以不结的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Dearie, you don't have to get married if you don't want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你想?\N{\fnArial\fs16}or do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是Chambers先生和Danielson小姐的伴娘\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm a bridesmaid in the Chambers-Danielson wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,遗憾 这款裙子超级萌人\N{\fnArial\fs16}Pity. They're such lovely dresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老天爷没怎么生给你一副翘臀\N{\fnArial\fs16}Nature didn't see fit to give you much in the way of hips,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是 亲爱的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}did she, dearie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉有点不舒服\N{\fnArial\fs16}I think I'm going to be ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会介意的吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Is that a problem for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,转身过来吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Turn around, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.77,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Scarlet 到那天你会变得更可人\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, Scarlet, you grow lovelier by the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会杀了你 再用这条裙子盖上你\N{\fnArial\fs16}I will kill you, and bury your body in this dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Daria?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,显而易见啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Isn't is obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,镇上阿拉伯酋长级土豪又买了几个老婆\N{\fnArial\fs16}An Arab sheik's in town to buy a few more wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,体育馆有一场婚博会 我们是模特\N{\fnArial\fs16}They're putting on a bridal expo in the gym. We're modeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,婚博会?\N{\fnArial\fs16}A bridal expo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真是会给高中小孩灌药啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's a good message to send to high school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是一场为课外活动集资的活动\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's a fundraiser for extracurricular activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我在捉摸什么样的课余活动\N{\fnArial\fs16}I wonder what kind of extracurricular activities
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,会引发婚礼...\N{\fnArial\fs16}would lead to a wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢? 要演话剧还是什么吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What about you? Are you in a play or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我要演林肯夫人 演疯了以后的她\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yes. I'm playing Mrs. Lincoln, after she went crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我没听说过她疯了耶\N{\fnArial\fs16}I didn't know she went crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有的 所以林肯才会饮弹自尽嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, yeah. That's why Lincoln shot himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,走啦 Brittany\N{\fnArial\fs16}Come on, Brittany.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.06,0:04:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去试完装\N{\fnArial\fs16}Let's finish out fitting,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟你讲林肯到底是怎么死掉的\N{\fnArial\fs16}and I'll tell you all about how nice Mr. Lincoln really died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,难道子弹没把他打死吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You mean the bullet didn't kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hold still.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你这身板儿可给我加了不少苦活儿呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm having a hard enough time with your body as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 全程羞辱到此画上圆满句号\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, I think my humiliation is complete now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真很搭我头发诶\N{\fnArial\fs16}It does match my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我那话说早了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I spoke too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,搞不懂你干嘛不让人家带高尔夫球杆\N{\fnArial\fs16}I don't know why you didn't let me bring my golf clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake 我们来看我家人 不是来玩好吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Jake, we're here to see my family, not to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这次陪你妹妹的又是那个男人?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Who's escorting your sister to this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她甩了那个雕刻家\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, she dumped the sculptor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,后来的跳伞教练也遭遇意外身亡了\N{\fnArial\fs16}the skydiving instructor had that horrible accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我估计那个Bruno就是临时葬礼陪衬\N{\fnArial\fs16}and I believe that Bruno is in some federal facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我也不造诶...\N{\fnArial\fs16}So I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们家Rita还真是选郎有方\N{\fnArial\fs16}That Rita sure knows how to pick 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,谋杀啊 谋杀啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Redrum! Redrum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\an8}语出惊悚片《闪灵》指酒店谋杀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你老妈这次可要下血本了\N{\fnArial\fs16}This will cost your mother a fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不然她也没处花她的票子了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, what else should she spend her money on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,难道要无聊到给她其他外甥女也交点教育基金嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Something boring, like college funds for her other granddaughters?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,全当给自己解心宽\N{\fnArial\fs16}I just keep telling myself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就当Erin没咱家俩宝出身好吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}that Erin hasn't had the advantages our girls have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,出身好?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Advantages?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我也纳闷\N{\fnArial\fs16}You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 被妹子们看见 我们就死定了\N{\fnArial\fs16}You know, if the girls see us, we're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,她们说 我们在场 她们会难为情的\N{\fnArial\fs16}They said we'd make them feel self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧? 她们想让我们来啦 哥们\N{\fnArial\fs16}Are you kidding? They want us to come, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,妹子想时 嘴上会说不要\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's why they told us not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,她们会觉得如果真邀请我们来婚博会\N{\fnArial\fs16}They knew that if they invited us to a bridal expo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们根本不会鸟她们的茬儿\N{\fnArial\fs16}there's no way we'd go near the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们来干嘛的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Then why are we here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,偷尝禁果啊 老兄 禁果啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Forbidden fruit, man. Forbidden fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你说话的时候 真心觉得自己过脑了么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}When you hear yourself talk, does it make sense to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔咯\N{\fnArial\fs16}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 小伙\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hey, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,提醒二位一下 我们很欢迎同性伴侣的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Just want you to know, we welcome same-sex partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要买戒指 你们自己看\N{\fnArial\fs16}What you do with the ring is your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这车可不便宜 开的时候当心点\N{\fnArial\fs16}This is an expensive vehicle. Be careful with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,行啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen\N{\fnArial\fs16}Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita\N{\fnArial\fs16}Rita!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗 Jake?\N{\fnArial\fs16}How are you, Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,也还不赖啦...\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, I'm not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,姑娘们真是可爱\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, the girls look lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可Daria\N{\fnArial\fs16}But Daria,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么没穿其他伴娘的那套礼服啊?\N{\fnArial\fs16}why didn't you get the same dress as the other bridesmaids?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,穿了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没参加彩排晚宴真是抱歉 Rita\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm sorry about the rehearsal dinner, Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天下午我开会开个没完\N{\fnArial\fs16}I had meetings all yesterday afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们要上路的时候...\N{\fnArial\fs16}and by the time we got on the road...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙 这是Paul 我男朋友\N{\fnArial\fs16}Everyone, this is Paul, my beau.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Paul Meyerson?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Paul Meyerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake? Jake和我是一个童子军团的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Jake? Jake and I were in Boy Scouts together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,带球杆了没?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You bring your clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,爸 你刚在车上说谁选郎有方来着?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Dad, what was that you said about knowing how to pick 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria...\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, Daria...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 那是谁啊?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wow, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy姨?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Aunt Amy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,刮车了没事\N{\fnArial\fs16}I don't mind a few dents,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但要是敢换电台 你就死定了\N{\fnArial\fs16}but change the radio station and you're a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy 好开心啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Amy, how delightful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为你不来了呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}I thought you weren't coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,本来没想\N{\fnArial\fs16}I wasn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.04,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不过想想你俩都能尽弃前嫌 我的话...\N{\fnArial\fs16}but I thought if you two could put aside years of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不过想想你俩都能尽弃前嫌 我的话...\N{\fnArial\fs16}bitterness and resentment, then so can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一天也无妨\N{\fnArial\fs16}for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy 看你在胡说八道什么了啦?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, Amy, why do you say such ridiculous things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你指说出口吗? Jake 还跟Helen过呢?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Out loud? So, Jake. You're still with Helen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不屈不挠 精神可嘉\N{\fnArial\fs16}Shows remarkable fortitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger 跳伞事业怎么样了?\N{\fnArial\fs16}And Roger. How's the skydiving going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy Roger过世了 这位是Paul\N{\fnArial\fs16}Amy, Roger passed away. This is Paul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 Paul 你好啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, sorry. Paul, how do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger谁啊?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Who's Roger?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他跳伞降落撞到牛\N{\fnArial\fs16}He fell onto a cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真是千千万之中的幸运儿\N{\fnArial\fs16}And he was one of the lucky ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子们\N{\fnArial\fs16}Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 不挖点槽点出来\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hey, what's the point of a senseless tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,无聊悲剧又意义何在呢?\N{\fnArial\fs16}if you can't find a little humor in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脑洞我喜欢 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs16}I like the way you think, Daria.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 Amy 我还没给你安排好座位呢...\N{\fnArial\fs16}Now, Amy, I'm not sure where we're going to seat you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我得喝一杯\N{\fnArial\fs16}I need a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,笑毛笑啊你?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 Amy姨好怪咖喔\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wow, Aunt Amy's really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.01,0:07:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Brian和Erin的婚礼不会下雨吧 千万不能啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, it can't rain on Brian and Erin's wedding. It just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那也太悲剧了 我可受不了\N{\fnArial\fs16}That would be so awful. I couldn't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,恰恰相反 雨是古代多子多孙的象征\N{\fnArial\fs16}On the contrary. Rain is an ancient symbol of fertility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,每对新人都该这么幸运\N{\fnArial\fs16}Every couple should be so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这还不知道嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一点小雨才不会破坏Brian和Erin的大喜日子呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}A little rain won't spoil the happiest day of Brian and Erin's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,外面或许是在下雨 可这里却是暖阳普照\N{\fnArial\fs16}It may rain out there, but in here the sun will be shinning
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正式下身地狱\N{\fnArial\fs16}We are now entering hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请确保胳膊和手肘不要伸出车窗外\N{\fnArial\fs16}Please keep your hands and elbows inside the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.38,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就是Erin表妹吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}You must be Erin's cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是 但Daira 她表妹那个...\N{\fnArial\fs16}I am. But Daria's, um, her cousin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啥?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\fnArial\fs16}Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样 我其实是受保护的证人\N{\fnArial\fs16}Actually, I'm in the witness protection program.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgendorffer一家善良地收养了我\N{\fnArial\fs16}The Morgendorffers were kind enough to take me in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我的亲生父母被暴徒残杀了\N{\fnArial\fs16}after my real family was exterminated by the mob.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你怎么没和我们穿同一款伴娘服啊?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, how come you didn't get the same dress as the rest of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,穿了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来 错过彩排晚宴真是你们的遗憾\N{\fnArial\fs16}Anyway, it's too bad you guys missed the rehearsal dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,超级好玩\N{\fnArial\fs16}It was so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你们去见护花使者吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Let me introduce you to your escorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria Quinn 这位是Garrett\N{\fnArial\fs16}Daria, Quinn, this is Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Garrett跟Quinn一对\N{\fnArial\fs16}Garrett will be with Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你真是我见过最萌人的小家伙儿\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn, you're just about the loveliest thing I ever saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fnArial\fs16}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能帮我去拿杯汽水\N{\fnArial\fs16}Do you think you could get me some soda
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只要那么一小小片的柠檬 谢谢啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}with just an eentsy-weentsy slice of lemon, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 这位是你男伴 Luhrman\N{\fnArial\fs16}Daria, this is your escort, Luhrman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊 Daryea\N{\fnArial\fs16}How do you do, Da-rye-a.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是Daria 好吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's Daria, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs16}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 Luhrman 是你的名还是你的姓?\N{\fnArial\fs16}So, Luhrman. Is that your first name or your last name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很重要吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他俩貌似很投机诶\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, they seem to be hitting it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她狂野 她泼辣 她可人\N{\fnArial\fs16}She's rough, she's tough, she's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,身着贝弗利山哈维斯出品真丝牛皮礼服的Sandi\N{\fnArial\fs16}Our Sandi is in a silk and rawhide outfit by Harve's of Beverly Hills,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,表现出人生最欢乐的时光并不一定灰暗无光\N{\fnArial\fs16}proving that the happiest day of your life doesn't have to be dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,举起手来 汉子们\N{\fnArial\fs16}Stick 'em up, hombres.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,下面是身着雷柏出品顺滑绸缎礼服的俏妞Brittany\N{\fnArial\fs16}Here's lovely Brittany in a sleeky and satiny number from Laburb
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好像在说\N{\fnArial\fs16}that says,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也许并非人家婚礼 去他的 我就是要跳舞\N{\fnArial\fs16}this may be my wedding day but, dammit, I wanna dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒 Brittany上台了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wake up! It's Brittany!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,啥? 诶 我去啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}What? Huh? Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似你让咱俩暴露了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I think you're blowing our cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kevin 你来这儿干嘛啊?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Kevin, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,惊喜呀 宝贝\N{\fnArial\fs16}Surprise, babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,值此分享...\N{\fnArial\fs16}And as we share...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这对年轻新人Brian和Eric喜结连理之时\N{\fnArial\fs16}the joy of this lovely young couple, Brian and Erin,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不得不追寻 爱是什么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}we are compelled to ask, what is love?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 爱 就像源自高山的一条小溪\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yes, love, like a tiny rivulet which begins in a high mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有历经千万英里的曲折蜿蜒\N{\fnArial\fs16}and only after twisting and turning for thousands of miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,克服无计其数的障碍\N{\fnArial\fs16}overcoming uncountable obstacles,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,最终得以相汇 合流\N{\fnArial\fs16}must eventually meet, and merge,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,融汇成广阔的爱情海\N{\fnArial\fs16}with that great ocean of love
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是与生俱来 也是命中注定\N{\fnArial\fs16}which is its birthright and its destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是她\N{\fnArial\fs16}It was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,宝贝 都说抱歉了嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}Babe, I said I was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要是现场有个超级星探怎么办?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What if there had been someone there from a major talent agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么赔?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那... 我猜他们已经见识到你的天赋了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, I guess they would've seen that you're talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是你猜的 不是吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, that's what you guess, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,更有可能人家猜到我跟混球之王谈恋爱\N{\fnArial\fs16}More like they would guess I'm dating the king of the jerks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,人家猜对了\N{\fnArial\fs16}and they'd be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快看看这些美丽的花喔\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wow! Look at all these flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是用来卖的还是用来摆的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Are these for sale or just display?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就跟我说\N{\fnArial\fs16}So they said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"我们就选你当副总裁\N{\fnArial\fs16}"Why don't we just make you VP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,掌管公司整体运作吧"\N{\fnArial\fs16}and have you take over the whole damn operation?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当时我刚刚29岁\N{\fnArial\fs16}And here I was, 29 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是 你说过了 话说你跟Rita咋认识的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, you mentioned. So, how'd you meet Rita?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的 我们都喜欢大海 我有艘帆船\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, you know, we both love the sea. I have a sailboat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她又有点呆\N{\fnArial\fs16}And she's a little dingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我开玩笑 别介意\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm kidding, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,认了也无妨\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, let's face it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita是有点轻浮 不过她可是床上猛虎\N{\fnArial\fs16}Rita's a little flighty, but she's a tiger in the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,继续满\N{\fnArial\fs16}Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 感觉她们家都有这病史\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, well, I guess it runs in the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才说什么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只是无关紧要的叨逼叨 没什么\N{\fnArial\fs16}Just a little pointless chit chat. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你要再来杯汽水吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Would you like another soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了\N{\fnArial\fs16}No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要不然咱俩分一瓶下水道清洗剂喝?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Or shall we just split a bottle of drain cleaner?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,搞清楚我的话只是开玩笑好吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Please be assured that my remark was intended in jest,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要煽动任何形式的自残行为\N{\fnArial\fs16}and not as an incitement to any type of self-destructive behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是本地人吧 对吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You're not from around here, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Daria 你在这啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Daria, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信我在婚礼前都没能见到你\N{\fnArial\fs16}I can't believe I didn't get to see you before the wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,婚礼办得特别好\N{\fnArial\fs16}It was a lovely ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.57,0:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没见过Brian吧 是不是超帅的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, but you haven't met Brian. Isn't he marvelous?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他在政府机关工作 搞情报的\N{\fnArial\fs16}He works for the government. Intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Erin\N{\fnArial\fs16}Erin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啦 知道啦 我什么都不该说的\N{\fnArial\fs16}I know, I know, I'm not supposed to say anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可就是厉害嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}but isn't it exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要是国家机密遭遇泄露\N{\fnArial\fs16}If our national security is compromised,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,追根究底肯定有个女人在作祟\N{\fnArial\fs16}you can bet there's a woman at the bottom of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老天啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 Daria\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hey, Daria,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么没穿其他伴娘的那款礼服?\N{\fnArial\fs16}how come you're not wearing the same dress as everybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,穿了 我要去一下...\N{\fnArial\fs16}I am. I think I'll go to the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小妞屋?\N{\fnArial\fs16}The little girl's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是 小妞屋\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, the little girl's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我去给鼻子打点粉 看下丝袜的破洞有没有变大\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm going to powder my nose and check the seams on my nylons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 你刚说你是做什么的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm sorry, what did you say you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我貌似听到搞情报的 但绝壁不可能\N{\fnArial\fs16}I thought I heard intelligence, but that can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,波涛汹涌 狂野的爱情之海\N{\fnArial\fs16}A wild, rolling, surging ocean of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,作为身只影单的个体 我们没办法掌控\N{\fnArial\fs16}on which we, as mere individuals, have no control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白我所说的话吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不太明白\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 Quinn 嗨 神父\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hi, Quinn. Hi, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我是个牧师 不是神父\N{\fnArial\fs16}Actually, I'm a minister, not a priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是\N{\fnArial\fs16}The important thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你是这个社区传颂美德的发声筒\N{\fnArial\fs16}you're the voice of morality in the community.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨穿正式礼服的自己 恨穿它的所有人\N{\fnArial\fs16}I hate myself in a formal dress, and everyone else, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你对这一套也不怎么感冒\N{\fnArial\fs16}You don't look too thrilled about things, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我为这场盛大的家庭宴会狂喜过头了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, no. I'm overjoyed to be at this big family event.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.89,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,每天的生活已经够辱人不倦了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Day to day life isn't humiliating enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你现在差不多上大学了吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Let's see, you're in college now, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不幸 还在高中\N{\fnArial\fs16}Still high school, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我对高中生活还有点模糊的记忆\N{\fnArial\fs16}I have some vague memories of high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现在 你们都随身带枪的 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}but these days, you all carry weapons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,像这种正式场合就不必了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, not to formal occasions like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你们这些小孩的失手之处\N{\fnArial\fs16}That's where you kids make your mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说\N{\fnArial\fs16}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,爱汝之友邻 爱汝之手足 爱汝之双亲\N{\fnArial\fs16}Love thy neighbors, love thy brother, love thy parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,每翻开新的一页 就去爱 爱 爱\N{\fnArial\fs16}Every time you turn a page, love, love, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为人过三十\N{\fnArial\fs16}I thought when I hit thirty
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会再在这种家庭活动上不得其所了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I would stop feeling out of place with these family things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得不得其所?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You feel out of place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你没发现我那俩姐们儿忙着互相攀比\N{\fnArial\fs16}You didn't notice my sisters are so busy competing with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我都进不了他们的雷达区么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}that I don't even register on their radar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是 可我还以为你都不在乎了呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}Yeah, but I just figured you were above all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 你蛮...\N{\fnArial\fs16}I mean, you're kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,酷?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你没法对我说出口\N{\fnArial\fs16}I know, you can't say that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,少年之约嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}Law of the teenagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的尊重\N{\fnArial\fs16}Thank you for respecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候 Helen和Rita一天到晚争风吃醋\N{\fnArial\fs16}When I was a kid, with Helen and Rita going at it all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,留下我一个人 就去做了体育解说员\N{\fnArial\fs16}all they left for me to do was to supply the color commentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,后来某天\N{\fnArial\fs16}Then, one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现我带着自己的一套世界观长大了\N{\fnArial\fs16}I found myself all grown up with my own point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.00,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,感到没有什么义务\N{\fnArial\fs16}and feeling no particular obligation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要听任何人扯淡 一直如此\N{\fnArial\fs16}to listen to anyone else's B.S. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,看来这套世界观效力蛮大的\N{\fnArial\fs16}So it actually worked out pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我得来婚礼见我姐们儿 是很强大\N{\fnArial\fs16}Unless I have to see my sisters at a wedding, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,神吐槽 一招吃遍天下\N{\fnArial\fs16}Sarcasm. It's a great way to deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这事你半点都不知道的 对吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}But, you wouldn't know anything about that, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 怎么了嘛?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事开始让我苦恼了\N{\fnArial\fs16}This whole thing is starting to get to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 Daria有道理\N{\fnArial\fs16}I mean, Daria had a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么高中生得想着"我要结婚"呢?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Why should high school kids be thinking about marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要是再看见可人女孩跟无脑笨蛋在一起...\N{\fnArial\fs16}If I see one more sweet, dopey girl stuck with a lame-brain idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,都不在啦啦队吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Not even the pep squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不在啦啦队\N{\fnArial\fs16}Not even the pep squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你老实说吧 Daphne 我根本没时间\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'll be honest with you, Daphne: I just can't find the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会?\N{\fnArial\fs16}How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这个... 首先我得工作\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, first of all, there's my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是脱衣舞女\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm an exotic dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在俱乐部那种\N{\fnArial\fs16}You know, at a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我会脱光衣服在陌生男人面前跳舞\N{\fnArial\fs16}I take my clothes off and dance for strange men.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这妹子真有一套\N{\fnArial\fs16}She's really very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过她?\N{\fnArial\fs16}You've seen her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去找一下Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'd better go check on Quinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢想象她现在忙活啥呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}I can't imagine what's keeping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不过真是一场不错的婚礼 不是吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, it was a lovely ceremony, though, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是的呢 Rita\N{\fnArial\fs16}It really was, Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就是可惜老妈不能过来\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm just so sorry Mom couldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不用担心 账单一寄到 她自会感同身受的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Don't worry, she'll get to live it all vicariously when the bills arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake 再帮我拿杯酒过来好吗?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Jake, how about getting me another glass of wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 亲爱的 还是不要...\N{\fnArial\fs16}Gee honey, maybe you shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Jake 赶紧给我拿杯酒过来\N{\fnArial\fs16}Jake, I'd really like an other glass of wine, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞\N{\fnArial\fs16}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen 你不是在挖苦我吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Helen, you're not bitter about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita 拜托 我挖苦你干嘛啦?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Rita, please. Why would I be bitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你和Erin就该得到最好的 你们一直是\N{\fnArial\fs16}You and Erin deserve the best. You always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是 我该被永世惩罚\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, no I should be punished forever
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我做了一些错误决定\N{\fnArial\fs16}because I made a few bad decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 你俩现在又在呛什么呢?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Hi. What are you two arguing about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,呛? 我俩才没呛架呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}Arguing? We're not arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还在生气爸给Rita买了豪爵\N{\fnArial\fs16}Still mad because Dad gave Rita that MG
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,却只给你买了普利茅斯·勇士?\N{\fnArial\fs16}and all you got was a Plymouth Valiant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 Amy 你真是什么都记得\N{\fnArial\fs16}My goodness, Amy, the things you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那款是道奇·达特\N{\fnArial\fs16}It was a Dodge Dart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我要说的是 Quinn\N{\fnArial\fs16}I guess what I'm trying to say, Quinn, is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能是个教士 但我也是个男人啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}I may be a man of the cloth, but I'm also a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Quinn 你在这啊 神父...\N{\fnArial\fs16}Quinn, there you are. Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我是牧师 不是神父\N{\fnArial\fs16}Actually, I'm a minister, not a priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都在问你去哪了呢\N{\fnArial\fs16}We've all been wondering where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我是的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, I know I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚在跟Quinn解释\N{\fnArial\fs16}I've just been explaining to Quinn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对于你们这样的年轻人 感情是多么的困惑\N{\fnArial\fs16}how emotions can be confusing for young people like yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我直言 神父\N{\fnArial\fs16}With all due respect, Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕你不属于怀有这种困惑情感的年轻人之列\N{\fnArial\fs16}I wonder if maybe you're not the one with the confusing emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你是什么意思\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm not sure I take your meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你懂的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, I think you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.97,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不要嘛\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢 原来只要稍加训练\N{\fnArial\fs16}So, it turns out that you could go through training and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.44,0:16:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要上空间站工作 只是不出三个月的事罢了\N{\fnArial\fs16}be up there working on the space station in under three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我在等我的太空饮料\N{\fnArial\fs16}Now I'm just waiting for my Tang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的是真的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wow. Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不是真的 全是我瞎编的\N{\fnArial\fs16}No, it's not true. I just made it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 我不是脱衣舞女 不懂海豹突击队\N{\fnArial\fs16}Also, I'm not an exotic dancer, I don't know Seal,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也没被深海鱼怪诱拐过\N{\fnArial\fs16}and I wasn't abducted by the undersea fish people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们觉得还是不要再跟你说话了\N{\fnArial\fs16}We decided we'd better not talk to you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我们不喜欢你啦 只是...\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's not that we don't like you. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你有点问题耶\N{\fnArial\fs16}You have problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, duh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你看咱们是不是该回去了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Honey, maybe we ought to think about getting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 我的小派对刚开始 服务生\N{\fnArial\fs16}No, my little party's just beginning. Waiter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 我给你拿点咖啡和婚礼蛋糕来\N{\fnArial\fs16}Here, I'll get you some coffee and wedding cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rita肯定爱死那一幕\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, Rita would love that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,亲眼看我在她面前长脂肪\N{\fnArial\fs16}seeing me balloon up right in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen 你说话声音有点大耶\N{\fnArial\fs16}Helen, um, you're being kind of loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,才没 你不会想当众吵架吧 啊?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, no! We don't want a scene, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会要破坏这好好的婚礼吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}We don't want to spoil the lovely wedding that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好好老妈可花了好好一笔银子呢 好不好?\N{\fnArial\fs16}lovely Mother spent so much lovely money on, do we.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,两位没什么事吧?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Is everything okay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事你说得倒是没错\N{\fnArial\fs16}Well, you were right about one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,某人确实选郎有方\N{\fnArial\fs16}she sure knows how to pick 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 听着 - 快别说了\N{\fnArial\fs16}- Hey, look! - Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢教训我?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Wanna make me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了 Helen?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What's going on? Helen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么会不知道发生了什么 老妈\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, you know perfectly well what's going on, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个悲剧男友想当众干架\N{\fnArial\fs16}Your pathetic boyfriend is making a scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你说悲剧是什么意思?\N{\fnArial\fs16}What do you mean pathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,照镜子就知道 伙计\N{\fnArial\fs16}Look in the mirror, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有一件事要说 Rita\N{\fnArial\fs16}I just want to say one thing, Rita.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能是漂亮的那个 可能是老妈宠着的那个\N{\fnArial\fs16}You may be the pretty one, you may be the one Mom loves,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但我特么会自力更生\N{\fnArial\fs16}but I worked my damn butt off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen姨 够啦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Aunt Helen! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么了? 不要拌鸡嘴 女士们\N{\fnArial\fs16}What's going on? No cat fights, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上嘴吧 你个史前低能儿\N{\fnArial\fs16}Shut the hell up, you prehistoric imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,情况越来越出位了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Things are getting ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以来个草率又不经意的露脸\N{\fnArial\fs16}I suggest we make a hasty but unobtrusive exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,走起 我们去找哪里有芝士薯条\N{\fnArial\fs16}Let's go find a place that serves cheese fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你吃 我看着\N{\fnArial\fs16}You eat, I'll watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我要离开一下\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm, uh, taking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好 留我在这看这帮疯狗\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, sure, leave me to the dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,想来就一起走咯\N{\fnArial\fs16}You can come if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 我想坐在这儿 看大屠杀怎么发展\N{\fnArial\fs16}No, I prefer to sit here and watch the carnage unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,和你相处很愉快\N{\fnArial\fs16}It's been fun, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好了啦 我也吃\N{\fnArial\fs16}Oh, all right, I'll eat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来 不要左顾右盼\N{\fnArial\fs16}Follow me. Don't look to the right or left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在对这些人爱莫能助\N{\fnArial\fs16}There's nothing you can do for these people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\an8}利威尔保龄球馆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方应该会有\N{\fnArial\fs16}This place oughta do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy姨\N{\fnArial\fs16}Aunt Amy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,叫Amy吧\N{\fnArial\fs16}Just Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy 人生一直这么庸俗白痴 辱人不倦\N{\fnArial\fs16}Amy, is life always tawdry, stupid, and humiliating,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还是只是阶段?\N{\fnArial\fs16}or is it just a phase?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,阶段而已\N{\fnArial\fs16}Just a phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在就盼着随时跳出这个阶段\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm expecting to grow out of it anytime now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,危险解除\N{\fnArial\fs16}Coast is clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,一夫三妻对这种猛烈的哺乳动物根本不是事儿\N{\fnArial\fs16}One three-time hubby is not enough for this red hot mammal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,稍后《呕心小世界》带来: 一夫多妻的河马酱\N{\fnArial\fs16}The polygamous hippopotamus, when Sick, Sad World returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会回去的 甭管是谁派你们来的\N{\fnArial\fs16}I'm not going back there. I don't care who sent you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这货眼熟么?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Does he look familiar to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\an8}摇滚乐队Ugly Kid Joe首张专辑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我貌似在《美国衰仔》里见过他\N{\fnArial\fs16}I think I saw him on America's Least Wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,估计你会想问我\N{\fnArial\fs16}I suppose you want to ask me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈小时候是什么样的\N{\fnArial\fs16}what your mother was like as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好呗 什么样的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Okay. What was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,超级无敌眼中钉\N{\fnArial\fs16}A tightly wound pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,换话题?\N{\fnArial\fs16}New topic?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你说咯\N{\fnArial\fs16}Name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我... 我都不知道发生了什么\N{\fnArial\fs16}I don't... I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我一张嘴和他说话 他就...\N{\fnArial\fs16}One minute I had him, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这里一切尽在掌控 长官们\N{\fnArial\fs16}Everything's under control here, officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,二位何不去买杯咖啡什么的 算我的\N{\fnArial\fs16}Why don't you two go have a cup of coffee or something, on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 我是受伤常客\N{\fnArial\fs16}Don't worry, I'm no stranger to pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你 Helen\N{\fnArial\fs16}I love you, Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你啊\N{\fnArial\fs16}I love you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 白天的时候来玩会不会更有趣呢?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Sir, wouldn't this be more enjoyable in the daytime?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,带几个小伙伴什么的?\N{\fnArial\fs16}Perhaps with some partners?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 小子 搞得灯光都晃悠了\N{\fnArial\fs16}Don't talk, son. You're shaking the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\fn迷你简汉真广标\fsp1\c&HF6FCF9&\pos(295,130)}欢迎微博关注\N\N{\fs25}@漫迪字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
